{"tid":792840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保安局：延長香港民族黨書面申述期限至9月11日","createTime":"2018-08-25T01:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T01:20:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6c95991c60564c4fe15dbf3619d49d771b4b13ff","tid":792840,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T01:20:26.000Z","msg":"政府再度延長香港民族黨作書面申述的期限，至9月11日或之前。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1414392-20180824.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1414392-20180824.htm&d=B7GgB8pnYMoULr9Hm87hWcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=56930677\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1414392-20180824.htm&h=a8abcb33\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1414392-20180824.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/2d/13718666_518552178343741_3243923722728034810_n.png/revision/latest?cb=20160912025756\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F2d%2F13718666_518552178343741_3243923722728034810_n.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20160912025756&h=14411311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方早前建議保安局局長引用《社團條例》，禁止香港民族黨運作，民族黨早前要求延長申述期限，獲局方延長至9月4日或之前作申述。保安局今次同意再度延長多一星期。<br />\n<br />\n保安局晚上回覆傳媒查詢時表示，香港民族黨發言人的代表律師早前致函保安局，要求延長該黨根據社團條例作書面申述的期限，保安局局長考慮後決定延長申述期，並已把有關決定通知香港民族黨。"}]}